M&S Hires Marcel Wanders to Design Homewares Range, FT Says

-- B y   S a r a h   J o n e s
-- 
2011-05-14T07:15:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-14/m-s-hires-marcel-wanders-to-design-homewares-range-ft-says.html
Marks & Spencer Group Plc has hired
Marcel Wanders, a Dutch industrial designer, to create a range
of gifts and homewares, the  Financial Times  reported, citing
people with knowledge of the matter.  The retailer declined to comment, the FT said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
